### ğŸ‘¥ 2. **Groups = Classrooms**

A *group* is like a **classroom** full of students.

* Many users can be inside **one group**.
* If you give permission to the **group**, all users inside it get the same access.

ğŸ‘‰ **Why create groups?**
So you can give permissions to **all developers at once**, instead of giving to each one.

